 services... Psychoeducational Assessment: Services include interdisciplinary assessment for children between the ages of 6 and 16 years old. Assessments evaluate a child's intellectual and learning abilities, speech and language concerns, and emotional or psychological challenges. Learn more about psychoeducational assessment services... Contact Us 1180 Union CircleDenton, TX 76203940-565-2066 Child and Family Resource Clinic Contact Information College of Education Matthews Hall, Room 214 1300 West Highland Street Denton, TX 76203 Contact the College of Education Email Us For technical problems with this web site, contact COEWeb@unt.edu.     UNT System UNT System UNT Dallas Campus UNT Health Science Center Universities Center at Dallas Disclaimer | AA/EOE/ADA | Privacy Statement | Web Accessibility Policy | State of Texas Online Go to Secure Login Page 